# Copy to .env for local development. .env is gitignored — never commit a real key.
#
# Free Gemini API key: https://aistudio.google.com/apikey
# Used only by the local diagnostic scripts (scripts/gemini-*.mjs). The shipped app
# never reads this: users paste their own key in Settings, and it is stored in their
# browser / their own Supabase row — no key is ever bundled into the site.
GEMINI_API_KEY=
